@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zgyojm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((v2 + tmp) * (wp.abs(v0 + 0.15) / wp.cos(v2 + 0.71)))
    v0 = (wp.cos(tmp) / tmp)
    v0 = ((0.69 - (v2 + 0.63 * tmp + 0.73)) - (wp.cos(v1 + 0.24) * wp.cos(tmp + 0.56)))
    v0 = (v0 - v0)
    v0 = wp.sin(v1)
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp + 0.57)) / ((v0 + 0.92 * v2 + 0.04) / 0.97))
    data[tid] = v0
